🔐 AUTH FLOW
Register → OTP → Verify → Login → JWT → Access APIs

🏢 COMPANY + VENDOR FLOW
Admin creates Company
        ↓
Vendor registers
        ↓
Admin approves vendor

🛍️ PRODUCT FLOW
Admin/Vendor → Create Product
       ↓
Assign Category + Pricing
       ↓
Visible in search/catalog


🛒 BUYING FLOW
Wishlist → Cart → Order

Detailed:

User adds product → Cart
      ↓
Order created
      ↓
Inventory checked


💳 PAYMENT FLOW
Order → Payment Initiated → Gateway → Verify → SUCCESS

OR

Order → Credit used → Ledger updated


🚚 LOGISTICS FLOW
Order → Warehouse selected
      ↓
Inventory reduced
      ↓
Shipment created
      ↓
Delivered


📄 INVOICE FLOW
Order Success → Invoice Generated


🔔 NOTIFICATION FLOW
Order → Notification
Payment → Notification
Shipment → Notification


📊 ANALYTICS FLOW
Order → Track revenue
User → Track activity


